{"id":635480,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/【立此存照】需要用摩斯电码交流的神奇国家/","date":"2020-02-15T06:37:17Z","modified":"2020-02-15T06:38:36Z","title":"【立此存照】“需要用摩斯电码交流的神奇国家”","content":"<p>2月13日，有新浪微博网友鉴于微博审查环境的日益严苛，创造性地在发消息时使用了<strong>摩斯电码</strong>以尝试躲避审查，阅读者需要将电码复制粘贴到<a href=\"http://www.matools.com/morse\">在线的页面</a>来进行内容解码。</p>\n<blockquote><p>摩尔斯电码（英语：Morse code）是一种时通时断的信号代码，通过不同的排列顺序来表达不同的英文字母、数字和标点符号。是由美国人艾尔菲德·维尔与萨缪尔·摩尔斯在1836年发明。（维基百科）</p></blockquote>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXFUYAA-WjP.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635482\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXFUYAA-WjP.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"974\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXFUYAA-WjP.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXFUYAA-WjP-139x300.jpeg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXFUYAA-WjP-473x1024.jpeg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXFUYAA-WjP-768x1662.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXFUYAA-WjP-710x1536.jpeg 710w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>该方法很快引来了其他网友的效仿，而一段内容被顶到了热评第一的位置：</p>\n<blockquote><p>&#8211;..-.&#8211;.&#8211;&#8230;./-..-.-.&#8212;&#8212;.&#8211;/&#8211;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;..-/-&#8230;-.-&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;/-&#8230;-.&#8212;.&#8212;.-./-&#8230;&#8230;&#8212;-.-.-./&#8212;.-.-..&#8211;&#8230;-/&#8212;&#8212;.&#8211;.-..&#8211;/&#8211;..&#8212;.-.&#8212;&#8211;/-..&#8212;&#8230;&#8230;&#8230;/-.-&#8230;-.-.&#8211;.-./-..&#8212;&#8230;.-..&#8211;/&#8211;..-.-..&#8212;&#8212;</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXJU0AAjrAV.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635485\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXJU0AAjrAV.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"974\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXJU0AAjrAV.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXJU0AAjrAV-139x300.jpeg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXJU0AAjrAV-473x1024.jpeg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXJU0AAjrAV-768x1662.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFXJU0AAjrAV-710x1536.jpeg 710w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>这段摩斯电码的解码内容是：</p>\n<blockquote><p>新闻、言论自由 结束一党专政</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFaiUcAE8J0A.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635486\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFaiUcAE8J0A.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"974\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFaiUcAE8J0A.jpeg 828w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFaiUcAE8J0A-139x300.jpeg 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFaiUcAE8J0A-473x1024.jpeg 473w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFaiUcAE8J0A-768x1662.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQrRFaiUcAE8J0A-710x1536.jpeg 710w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>不过，令人遗憾的是，中国可能是第一个让网友“需要用摩斯电码交流的神奇国家”，同样也是第一个可以对“摩斯电码”进行内容审查的国家：</p>\n<p>例如有网友就表示，在微信群使用摩斯电码进行交流，导致了被封群封号。这或许说明摩斯电码是很容易被审查的。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQtE4HRUYAANQB2-1.jpeg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-635484\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQtE4HRUYAANQB2-1.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQtE4HRUYAANQB2-1.jpeg 1152w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQtE4HRUYAANQB2-1-169x300.jpeg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQtE4HRUYAANQB2-1-576x1024.jpeg 576w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQtE4HRUYAANQB2-1-768x1365.jpeg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQtE4HRUYAANQB2-1-864x1536.jpeg 864w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2020/02/EQtE4HRUYAANQB2-1-1080x1920.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有推特网友就此表示“常见的这种可逆算法就是透明的。” 而截至发稿时，进行此测试的微博网友 @天长地久有时翠 以及热评第一的 @烟斗国父1 疑似已遭微博封号，新浪微博ID搜索查无结果。</p>\n<p>消息<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BoroChina/status/1228023772139048960\">来源</a></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">需要用摩斯电码交流的神奇国家<br />（图三：热评第一解码） <a href=\"https://t.co/C2V9c24F8Y\">pic.twitter.com/C2V9c24F8Y</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Aki アキ ヤーン (@BoroChina) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/BoroChina/status/1228023772139048960?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 13, 2020</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"mD8JuG5Cba\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e7%bf%a0%e4%b8%8e%e7%a5%88%e7%bf%a0%e8%b6%85%e8%af%9d/\">【敏感词库】“翠”与“祈翠超话”</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe title=\"《【敏感词库】“翠”与“祈翠超话”》—中国数字时代\" class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2020/02/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e7%bf%a0%e4%b8%8e%e7%a5%88%e7%bf%a0%e8%b6%85%e8%af%9d/embed/#?secret=mD8JuG5Cba\" data-secret=\"mD8JuG5Cba\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\" frameborder=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\"></iframe></p>\n","author":1015,"categories":[18271,38912,39707],"tags":[9249,9283,8859,39648,9212,39789]}